# Advanced Features Demonstration Script - Rugby Edition
new-tournament SixNationsElite rugby
add-stage round-robin Groups
# Use set-policy to change the standings to knockout-progression in DRAFT state
set-policy Groups standings knockout-progression

# Create custom teams
create-team AllBlacks
add-player AllBlacks P1 PROP 1
add-player AllBlacks P2 HOOKER 2
add-player AllBlacks P3 PROP 3
add-player AllBlacks P4 PROP 4
add-player AllBlacks P5 PROP 5
add-player AllBlacks P6 PROP 6
add-player AllBlacks P7 PROP 7
add-player AllBlacks P8 PROP 8
add-player AllBlacks P9 SCRUM_HALF 9
add-player AllBlacks P10 FLY_HALF 10
add-player AllBlacks P11 FLY_HALF 11
add-player AllBlacks P12 FLY_HALF 12
add-player AllBlacks P13 FLY_HALF 13
add-player AllBlacks P14 FLY_HALF 14
add-player AllBlacks P15 FLY_HALF 15
add-player AllBlacks Bench16 FLY_HALF 16
register AllBlacks

# Register auto-generated team
register Wallabies
close-registration
publish

# Show team to see roster
show team AllBlacks

start-tournament
start-match next

# Try + Conversion by specific player P10
action try AllBlacks P10 15
action conversion AllBlacks P10 16

# Opponent scores a penalty kick
action penalty Wallabies 30

# Substitute P10 for Bench16
substitute AllBlacks P10 Bench16 40

# Action revoked - Let's do a statistical action instead since we can't guess UUID easily for script
action knock-on Wallabies 42

# Injury to P9!
injury AllBlacks P9 2 "Concussion" 44

finish-period

# Show match details at half time
show match

# Second half
action scrum-won AllBlacks P1 50
action yellow AllBlacks P2 51

# Disqualify the opponent!
disqualify Wallabies

finish-period

# The match is over (or ended early by walkover depending on engine).
# Show matches to see the walkover status
show matches

advance-stage
show standings
quit
